<plot>On the run from a loan shark, Saul (Steven Milling) ventures alone to Los Angeles looking for a fresh start. On his first day in town, he falls for an artist named Ricki (Shari Baltau) and finds work. The "job" turns out to be running drugs for Dealer Johnny (Daniel Cohn) who is wanted in two states. Can Saul untangle himself from another bad situation? Sometimes the only way out is through sacrifice, even if it means saying goodbye....again.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?470719</url></doc>
